<title>WORK FOR THE NIGHT IS COMING</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Zan hung tung ina, sem un,
 Zingkal in sem pan un;
 Zing dai laka le sem un,
 Zing pakcha lakah;
 Ni san tieng inle sem un,
 Sun hun inle sem un;
 Zan hung tung ina sem un,
 Chawlh phat a tun man.

[V2]
 2. Zan hung tung ina, sem un,
 Nisa pi nuoi ale;
 Phat cheng nasep nan mangun,
 Chawlh phat hi pai ding;
 Mitphet kal a hun chieh zel,
 Thilpha khawl nan mangun;
 Zan hung tung ina, sem un,
 Na sep theih lai un.

[V3]
 3. Zan hung tung in, na sem un,
 Nisa tum nung inle;
 Khawvak a um lai chanin,
 Semun, a beih man;
 Vak kit ngei talo dinga,
 Khawvak beih man sem un;
 Zan hun tung ina, sem un,
 Na sep zawh ma cheng.</lyrics>
</song>